Diana King (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diana_King_(actress) 0 Diana King (2 August 1918 – 31 July 1986) was an English actress who had a career on British television from 1939 to 1986. Born in Buckinghamshire, she was sometimes credited as Diane King. Diana_King ( 2_August_1918 – 31_July_1986 ) was an_English_actress who had a_career on British_television from 1939 to 1986 .
